DeskSoft EarthTime 5.11 A handy program, helps to display the local time and date of any place of our large Globe. The application has a good built-in database for 3000 cities, and if necessary, the user can add their own, download EarthTime can be lower. 
Of the additional is worth noting support for setting the alarm at any local time, plus you get a large number of time zone settings and local time. EarthTime displays the Earth in both the night and day view, you can view the map in full screen mode. br / & gt;
